Project 2 
Sprint 2 Report

Overall Design Concept: 
Connections used from the controller to the devices:
I2C: GPS, IMU
UART: Bluetooth
What we used for programming:
Circuit Python: GPS, IMU
MicroPython: Bluetooth 


Parts List
Controller: Raspberry Pi Pico
GPS: Adafruit Mini GPS PA1010D 
IMU: Adafruit BNO055 Absolute Orientation Sensor
Bluetooth: DSD Tech HC-05 
SD Card Adapter: Micro SD Card Adapter Module
Android device 
GeeekPi UPS Power Supply Uninterruptible UPS HAT for Raspberry Pi Pico
18650 Rechargeable Battery 9900mAh 3.7Volt Large Capacity


Plan Going Forward:
integrating the codes from each component.
developing the graphical user interface.
Start a design for the PCB and the case
Final testing 
